  "en": "<div class=\"mb-8\"><img src=\"/images/christian-divorce-case.jpg\" alt=\"Historic Court Ruling - Khul' for Christian Woman in Egypt\" class=\"w-full max-w-lg mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-4\" /><p class=\"text-center text-sm text-gray-400 italic\">Historic Legal Precedent in Christian Personal Status Cases in Egypt</p></div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#c8a876] mb-4\">Historic Legal Precedent: Khul' Ruling for Christian Woman in Egypt</h2><p class=\"mb-6\">In a first-of-its-kind move, one of the clients of <strong>Karim El-Dib Law Firm</strong> obtained a khul' (divorce) ruling for a Christian woman, in a legal precedent that embodies the evolution of the concept of justice within personal status cases in Egypt.</p><div class=\"bg-[#c8a876]/10 border-r-4 border-[#c8a876] p-4 mb-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-[#c8a876] mb-2\">โ๏ธ Case Summary</h3><p class=\"text-sm\">Historic court ruling granting khul' to a Christian woman, based on the new draft law for Christian personal status, with full respect for Christian law and church teachings.</p></div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#c8a876] mb-4\">Legal Basis of the Ruling</h2><p class=\"mb-4\">The ruling was issued based on:</p><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside mb-6 space-y-2\"><li><strong>New Draft Law for Christian Personal Status</strong>: Aimed at organizing family relations fairly</li><li><strong>Proof of impossibility of continuing marital life</strong>: Through factual evidence and testimony</li><li><strong>Occurrence of severe psychological harm to the wife</strong>: Documented with medical and psychological reports</li><li><strong>Respect for religious principles</strong>: While preserving Christian law teachings</li></ul><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#c8a876] mb-4\">Importance of This Legal Precedent</h2><p class=\"mb-4\">This ruling represents a qualitative shift in the family justice system for Christians in Egypt:</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6\"><div clas